Idea for an App: Home Organizer with Option to Sell Used Items Online
text:
I have a lot of items in self-storage. Currently I use a barcode app (Duck Pack & Track). It allows you to assign barcode to a box of items and assign a list of items in the box with pictures. It's little clumsy.

It would be nice to have an app where you can:

- assign a a barcode to individual items with photos, item description, location - search items by description, tag, groupings, location - have a recognition of item by taking a photo, generate a generic description based on photo - easily submit unwanted items to sites like ebay or facebook marketplace for free or for sale - should be able to have tags, search by tags, browse pictures - should be self contained, Duck Pack & Track uses drop box to store some data
